The paper focuses on improving video delivery over the internet, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the design of a scheduler, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses the trade-off between video quality and cost, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SD) and information theory (cs.IT).
